      <string id="unknown_8">This policy controls custom banner text and custom foreground/background colors. It writes CustomSettings plus CustomDisplayText, CustomBackgroundColor, and CustomForeColor under HKLM\SOFTWARE\Policies\NetBannerNG.

If this policy is Enabled, NetBannerNG uses the custom text and color values from this policy. When enabled, the composed banner text uses the selected classification as a base and appends the custom display text; Caveats text from the Caveats policy is not appended.

If this policy is Disabled or Not Configured, NetBannerNG does not use custom text/colors from this policy and falls back to catalog-based colors and standard text composition.</string>
      <string id="SizeMessage">40 Characters Max</string>

